{"word":"G1396 - δουλαγωγέω - doulagōgéō - doo-lag-ogue-eh'-o - Bring into subjection","slug":"G1396","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">δουλαγωγέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>doulagōgéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>doo-lag-ogue-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Bring into subjection"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B4;&#x03BF;&#x03C5;&#x03BB;&#x03B1;&#x03B3;&#x03C9;&#x03B3;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - doulago&#x0304;geo&#x0304;</b> - <i>doo-lag-ogue-eh'-o</i><p/>From a presumed compound of <a href=\"#/G1401\">G1401</a> and <a href=\"#/G71\">G71</a>; to <i>be a slave driver</i>, that is, to <i>enslave</i> (figuratively <i>subdue</i>): - bring into subjection."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1397\">G1397</a>, <a href=\"#/G1398\">G1398</a>, <a href=\"#/G1399\">G1399</a>, <a href=\"#/G1401\">G1401</a>, <a href=\"#/G1402\">G1402</a>, <a href=\"#/G2615\">G2615</a>, <a href=\"#/G3787\">G3787</a>, <a href=\"#/G4889\">G4889</a>"}]}